The Nigeria Centre for Disease Control (NCDC), has confirmed ten new cases of Novel Coronavirus (COVID-19) in the country. The NCDC said that  ten new cases of #COVID19 have been reported in Nigeria: 6 in Lagos, 2 in FCT and 2 in Edo. As at 11:15 am 5th April there are 224 confirmed cases of #COVID19 reported in Nigeria. Twenty-seven have been discharged with five deaths 